---
source: crates/loom/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: "loom_help(&[\"note\", \"set\"])"
---
Replace all notes for the spec

Usage: loom note set [OPTIONS] --json <JSON> <LABEL>

Arguments:
  <LABEL>  Spec label

Options:
      --json <JSON>       JSON array of note strings: `'["note 1", "note 2"]'`
  -w, --workspace <PATH>  Workspace root. Defaults to the current working directory
  -A, --agent <BACKEND>   Override the agent backend for this invocation [possible values: claude, pi]
      --kind <KIND>       Note kind [default: implementation]
  -h, --help              Print help
